                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">Any visitor to our site is covered by our Privacy Policy(s). This policy applies to the collection, storage, processing, and transfer of Personal Information both online and offline.</p>
                    <h3 class="text-[#a51f24] lg:text-[28px] md:text-[20px] text-[14px] font-[500] sitka mb-2 relative before:content-[''] before:w-20 before:h-[4px] before:bg-[#000000] before:absolute before:bottom-0">Definitions</h3>
                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">The following words have the following meanings in this Privacy Policy:</p>
