                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">"Marketing Information" refers to the Organization's collection, use, and disclosure of your Web Analytical Information and Personal Information, such as your name, address, e-mail address, and telephone number, for marketing and promotional purposes as described in this Privacy Policy.</p>
                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">"Personal Information" refers to data that may be used to identify a specific person, either alone or in combination, and includes financial data.</p>
                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">The Organization's website, https://vanguardpublisher.com/, as well as any other Organization-controlled or approved Sites (including, without limitation, any Business Associate sites), are referred to as "Site" or "Sites," regardless of domain name or IP address.</p>
