                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">We use marketing information to help us better plan our Sites and services to meet your needs; to measure and improve the services and features of our Site(s); to communicate with you about products or services that may be of interest to you via e-mail, postal mail, telephone, cellular/mobile phone, PDA devices, and/or on applications for mobile phones such as iPhone or Blackberry; and to provide you with cues. We also employ a number of technical mechanisms to identify and respond to unusual behavior, as well as to screen material to avoid abuses such as spam. Some users' Site functionality may be permanently suspended or terminated as a result of these actions.</p>
                    <h3 class="text-[#a51f24] lg:text-[28px] md:text-[20px] text-[14px] font-[500] sitka mb-2 relative before:content-[''] before:w-20 before:h-[4px] before:bg-[#000000] before:absolute before:bottom-0">Information about yourself</h3>
                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">The Organization understands that by entrusting us with your Personal Information, you are expressing your faith in us, and we value that confidence. Your Personal Information will not be sold, rented, or leased to anyone else. We may collect, use, and disclose Personal Information for the following reasons:</p>

                    <ul class="pl-3 list-disc mb-2 mt-2">
