                        <li class="font-medium"> to respond to your inquiries</li>
                        <li class="font-medium"> to administer promotions in which you have expressed an interest</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">for our internal marketing purposes, which may include, but is not limited to, sending you material about products, services, updates, and other information that we believe may be of interest to you</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">for using Social Networks to promote communication and collaboration among members of the Organization's community</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">to share with our Partners who may contact you about their services;</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">to share with our Partners or Business Associates who execute services on our behalf</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">to examine how people use and access websites and services;</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">to enhance the performance and delivery of the site and services</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">to examine academic and learning results, as well as personal preferences</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">to assess risk and business outcomes</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">to collect money for the services we give you</li>
                        <li class="font-medium">to keep company documents for a reasonable amount of time</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">We may utilize an automatic telephone dialing system, artificial or prerecorded voice messages, or text messaging to provide you with different communications in conjunction with the uses set out above. Furthermore, by giving us with a cellular, wireless, or mobile telephone number as your contact number, you agree to give us your express agreement to receive automated dialing system calls, prerecorded voice messages, or text messages connected to your registration. Please give us with a LAN-based telephone number if you do not want to receive these updates on your cellular or mobile phone.</p>
                    <h3 class="text-[#a51f24] lg:text-[28px] md:text-[20px] text-[14px] font-[500] sitka mb-2 relative before:content-[''] before:w-20 before:h-[4px] before:bg-[#000000] before:absolute before:bottom-0">Financial Information</h3>
                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">Your financial information will be used to offer the products and services you have requested, to analyze operational and business performance, to assess risk, and to complete your registration or other transaction with us. Except in the event of a reorganization, merger, or purchase of our shares or assets, it will not be sold, rented, or otherwise transferred to an Educational Partner, Business Associate, or Unrelated Entity for any other reason.</p>
                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">To secure your credit card information sent to us over the Internet, we employ Secure Socket Layer (SSL) 128-bit encryption. No one, not even our employees, has access to your payment card information.</p>

