                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">On our Sites, we utilize cookies, web beacons, and other related internet technologies to enable us to carry out the purposes outlined above, as well as to provide Sites message and keep track of your Information. These little fragments of program code can be deleted from your computer and browser. You may disable such technologies if you choose, but this may make our Sites inaccessible to you. By deactivating these capabilities in your browser software, you may opt out of cookies and other internet technologies. If you need help altering cookie settings or deleting cookie files, go to your browser's "Help" option.</p>
