                    <p class="mb-2 font-medium">The problem of children's privacy is one that we take very seriously. Our websites are not intended for or directed towards minors under the age of thirteen. You can contact us or delete the information yourself if you feel your kid has given us with Personal Information or registered at one of our Sites and would like it removed.</p>
